item.title: Relearning Music
item.description: I’ve been playing guitar since I was 10, I think. I picked at 15 when I performed two of the hardest songs I ever tried Hotel california A river flows in you - Sungha Jung arrangement Since then little effort I made to make progress. So why then I want to relearn music now and what is the meaning of relearn? I learned guitar in a very rustic way: picked up a song I liked and them tried to reproduce it.
